<div class="row">
  <div class="span12" id="logo">
    <%= image_tag asset_path('logo.jpg') %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="span12">
    <h1>Welcome to Spartups!</h1>
    <p>
    Spartups is a community initiative launched in San Jose, CA that
    connects first-time and experienced entrepreneurs together to
    collaborate on projects they are passionate about, while providing them
    with whatever resources they need to be successful.
    </p>
    <a href="about.html" class="btn btn-primary">Learn more</a>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="span3">
    <h2>Have an idea?</h2>
    <p>
    Spartups can help you find the resources to build it. Attend one of
    our meetings to pitch your idea in front of other entrepreneurs just
    like yourself, and we'll help you form a team to launch your idea
    from concept to market!
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="span3">
    <h2>Already working on startup?</h2>
    <p>
    Spartups can help you find resources to take your startup to the next
    level. Whether you need to find mentors or advisors to guide you, or
    investors to give you that little financial push - our network can
    help you grow!
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="span3">
    <h2>Looking for your next investment?</h2>
    <p>
    The Spartups network is full of promising startup projects that have
    the potential to become the next big thing. Why not attend one of our
    meetings to meet these talented entrepreneurs - We're certain you'll
    find at least a few that you'll want to invest in!
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="span3">
    <h2>Speak at our event?</h2>
    <p>
    Interested in partnering with Spartups or being a guest speaker at
    our next event?
    </p>
    <a href="mailto:saif@spartups.com" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
  </div>
</div>
